  "body": "- [x] I've [opened a support ticket](https://trufflesuite.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\nzendesk ticket number: 523516\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nWhile writing tests for my contract using TypeScript, I want to import a type into my test file as follows:\r\n```\r\nimport { DotTokenInstance } from '../generated';\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, I get the following error when running `truffle test`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nUsing network 'development'.\r\n\r\nCompiling your contracts...\r\n===========================\r\n> Everything is up to date, there is nothing to compile.\r\n\r\n/Users/chriskrogh/dev/dot/token/test/DotToken.test.ts:1\r\nimport { DotTokenInstance } from '../generated';\r\n^^^^^^\r\n\r\nSyntaxError: Cannot use import statement outside a module\r\nat compileFunction (<anonymous>)\r\nat Object.compileFunction (node:vm:353:18)\r\nat wrapSafe (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1039:15)\r\nat Module._compile (node:internal/modules/cjs/loader:1073:27)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI have tried modifying the mocha config in `truffle-config.js` to be\r\n```\r\nmocha: {\r\nÂ  require: ['ts-node/register'],\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nand adding a `tsconfig.testing.json` with\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\nÂ  \"compilerOptions\": {\r\nÂ  Â  \"module\": \"commonjs\",\r\nÂ  Â  \"target\": \"es6\"\r\nÂ  },\r\nÂ  \"include\": [\"test/**/*.test.ts\"]\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nhowever this did not work. I also tried modifying the mocha config to includeÂ \r\n\r\n```\r\nmocha: {\r\nÂ  require: ['@babel/register'],\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nand following the babel installation instructions here [babel](https://babeljs.io/en/setup?fireglass_rsn=true#installation), however that did not work either.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n- Create a new truffle project using `truffle init`\r\n- Create a TypeScript test file `*.test.ts`\r\n- Import a module into the test file using `import a from 'path/to/a'` syntax\r\n- Run `truffle test`\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe test should run.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nThe exception outlined above is thrown.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: \r\n* Ethereum client: ganache-cli\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): Truffle v5.4.19 (core: 5.4.19)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v16.3.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 7.15.1\r\n",
